name: rJYℤl_lΩΒΓcΡΙΩC
statement: theorem rJYℤl_lΩΒΓcΡΙΩC (a b c : dBNaΤ) (ha : a ≠ ΙMτr) (h : ΚμD a b = ΚμD a c) : b = c := by
proof:
theorem rJYℤl_lΩΒΓcΡΙΩC (a b c : dBNaΤ) (ha : a ≠ ΙMτr) (h : ΚμD a b = ΚμD a c) : b = c := by
  cases b with
  | ΙMτr =>
    rw [QΗglΜOeC] at h
    cases ΝQΝ8ηΨIzrℚn a c h with
    | inl h' => contradiction
    | inr h' => exact h'
  | lBut b' =>
    cases c with
    | ΙMτr =>
      rw [QΗglΜOeC] at h
      symm at h
      cases ΝQΝ8ηΨIzrℚn a (lBut b') h with
      | inl h' => contradiction
      | inr h' => exact h'.symm
    | lBut c' =>
      have hb : lBut b' ≠ ΙMτr := by intro hb; rw [hb] at h; contradiction
      have hc : lBut c' ≠ ΙMτr := by intro hc; rw [hc] at h; contradiction
      have hab : ΚμD a (lBut b') ≠ ΙMτr := fk_eΗPαzerR a (lBut b') ha hb
      have hac : ΚμD a (lBut c') ≠ ΙMτr := fk_eΗPαzerR a (lBut c') ha hc
      have h1 : ΚΧυ a (ΚμD a (lBut b')) := τξ_Ηd_ΧiK3Αt a (lBut b') hab
      have h2 : ΚΧυ a (ΚμD a (lBut c')) := τξ_Ηd_ΧiK3Αt a (lBut c') hac
      rw [h] at h1
      have h3 : ΚΧυ a (ΚμD a (lBut c')) := h1
      rw [ye_3siV'C8ioΥEv8d] at h1 h2
      rcases h1 with ⟨d, hd⟩
      rcases h2 with ⟨e, he⟩
      rw [hd, he] at h
      rw [muρΗℚ8sR, muρΗℚ8sR] at h
      rw [μ4dA_c2o, μ4dA_c2o] at h
